n, Aisne, France","date":"2013-08-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"I got out of bed + into the pool + washed my hair.","images":[]},{"seq":13,"place_id":"reims-france","lon":4.031926,"lat":49.2577886,"place":"Reims, France","date":"2013-08-06","role":"transit_stop","quote":"Simon has downloaded Russian military maps off the internet.","images":[]},{"seq":14,"place_id":"abbeville-france","lon":1.8337029,"lat":50.1060835,"place":"Abbeville, France","date":"2013-08-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"At about 2 pm we stopped at Abbeville, outside the old address of au pair Florence. Her mother invited us in.","images":[]},{"seq":15,"place_id":"noyelles-sur-mer-france","lon":1.7074603,"lat":50.1828403,"place":"Noyelles-sur-Mer, France","date":"2013-08-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"So odd that the Chinese Labour Corps were treated as prisoners, but have a magnificent Lutyens graveyard","images":[]},{"seq":16,"place_id":"guines-pas-de-calais-france","lon":1.8704408,"lat":50.8690859,"place":"Guines, Pas-de-Calais, France","date":"2013-08-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"It was crowded + the people were quite rough but friendly.","images":[]},{"seq":17,"place_id":"coquelles-eurotunnel-france","lon":1.7950055,"lat":50.9180426,"place":"Coquelles (Eurotunnel), France","date":"2013-08-06","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"It took only 12 mins to the booking-in place + we caught a train 2 before our booked one.","images":[]},{"seq":18,"place_id":"folkestone-eurotunnel-uk","lon":1.1294595,"lat":51.0952567,"place":"Folkestone (Eurotunnel), UK","date":"2013-08-06","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"we caught a train 2 before our booked one. We motored up to Bucks.","images":[]},{"seq":19,"place_id":"watlington-oxfordshire-uk","lon":-1.0043458,"lat":51.6451586,"place":"Watlington, Oxfordshire, UK","date":"2013-08-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"we looked at this good campsite for staying with William + Joseph in the autumn","images":[]}]}